About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: GINGER CHICKEN | 500 Chicken Legs With Ginger | Traditional Ginger Chicken Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook ginger chicken recipe by using 500 chicken legs and a huge amount of ginger. We first cut and fried the ginger separately. Then, we marinate the chicken in curd and lemon juice. Finally, we cook them all together.

The taste is delicious!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 06 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 9th December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir

Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya

Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta

Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

snippet.description:
Thankamani is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language crime thriller film written and directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan and Produced by R B Choudhry under the banner of Super Good Films in association with Iffaar Media Raaffi Mathirra. The film stars Dileep and is based on a real-life incident that occurred in Thankamany in October 1986. Thankamani Music Rights has been acquired by Saina Music.

snippet.description:

Episode 3949: Sodhi's Anniversary
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu tosses a ball towards Jetha, but he misses it, and the ball lands on the wall. Champaklal is furious at both of them for playing with the ball inside. Later, Jetha tries to conceal the fact that he failed to pay a client. Jetha rushes out of the home before Champaklal can interrogate him. Babita unintentionally calls Jethalal, and he is apprehended by Champaklal.
 
Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Despite the significant investment of 4000 crores, the stormwater drainage project faced its ultimate test during Michaung Cyclone.  Here we discuss about critically assess the design, execution, and efficacy of the project, shedding light on the areas where it fell short and left Chennai vulnerable.  Here we also discussed the solution to solve flood issues during cyclones.

snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong : The New Empire | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in theaters 2024

The epic battle continues!  Legendary Pictures‚Äô cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence‚Äîand our own. ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire‚Äù delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard.  The film stars Rebecca Hall (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù The Night House‚Äù), Brian Tyree Henry (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), Dan Stevens (‚ÄúGaslit,‚Äù ‚ÄúLegion,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), Kaylee Hottle (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù), Alex Ferns (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúWrath of Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúChernobyl‚Äù) and Fala Chen (‚ÄúIrma Vep,‚Äù ‚ÄúShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù the ‚ÄúPirates of the Caribbean‚Äù series) and Simon Barrett (‚ÄúYou‚Äôre Next‚Äù) and Jeremy Slater (‚ÄúMoon Knight‚Äù), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd..  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni and Brian Rogers.  The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira. 

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúWorld War Z‚Äù), production designer Tom Hammock (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúX,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Guest‚Äù), editor Josh Schaeffer (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMolly‚Äôs Game‚Äù), costume designer Emily Seresin (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop of the Lake‚Äù).  The composers are Tom Holkenborg (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSonic the Hedgehog‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.‚Äù  It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on April 12, 2024 and beginning 10 April 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.

Nattu Kaka and Bagha convinced Jethalal to give them the contract for construction in Gokuldham Society. Jetha informs everyone in the society about the same. But instead, he gets the biggest shock. What will Jethalal do now? Will the construction work finally begin?

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Salaar Hindi Trailer | Prabhas | Prashanth Neel | Prithviraj|Shruthi|Hombale Films| Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
Please‚Ä¶I‚Ä¶Kindly‚Ä¶Request!üî•
Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

snippet.title: Dating Mausi Ki Student - Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi (Crowd Work Video)
snippet.description:
Hello Doston,

Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy crowd work video:
Dating Mausi Ki Student which was recorded in my comedy show called BEST OF GUPTAJI.

This is a New Stand Up Comedy video which we have recorded in October at The Comedy Theatre, Gurgoan

Hope you enjoy this latest comedy video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai and Genuinely, I am presenting my new show with an old name Best of GuptaJi which I am starting to tour now.
Why Best of GuptaJi? because I want all the content in my show to be the best content from my side. So if you have seen my videos on chai, maggi, hotel, airport, tinder, starbucks etc, it was a part of Best of GuptaJi only so am trying to give you new content but with that level only.

If you want to come for the Best of GuptaJi tour, here is the ticket link : https://linktr.ee/appurvgupta

Book Now as we have limited seats in every city.

Thank You for watching Videos of Indian Stand Up Comedian Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3948 | 7 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3948: Sakharam Ko Lagi Chot
--------------------------------------------------------
Tappu and his friends play badminton near his scooter i.e. Sakharam. Unfortunately, Goli falls over Sakharam. Bhide gets angry at Tapu Sena for playing badminton near Sakhram. He confronts Tappu Sena and asks them to play somewhere else. Gokuldham residents denied his request and ask him to find another place for parking Sakharam.  Later, Roshan receives a piece of good news. What happens next? Watch the episode to know more!!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3948, 7 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
